msgid "OUYA controller"
msgstr "Ovladač OUYA"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The OUYA is a crowd-funded Android-based microconsole released in 2013. The OUYA controller includes a single-touch touchpad in the center of the controller."
msgstr "OUYA je mikrokonzole založená na Androidu a financovaná crowdfundingem, vydaná v roce 2013. Ovladač OUYA obsahuje uprostřed jednotykový touchpad."

